This is source code of my slasyz.ru page.

  * Python:
      * Django (https://www.djangoproject.com/)
      * django-precise-bbcode (https://github.com/slasyz/django-precise-bbcode)
      * mysqlclient (https://github.com/PyMySQL/mysqlclient-python)
      * Pillow (https://python-pillow.github.io/)

  * Node.js:
      * gulp (http://gulpjs.com/)
      * gulp-rename (https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-rename)
      * gulp-sass (https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-sass)
      * gulp-uglify (https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-uglify)
      * del (https://www.npmjs.com/package/del)

  * Bower:
      * Zurb Foundation (http://foundation.zurb.com/)
      * jQuery (https://jquery.com/)

How to deploy the project:

  * install python, setup virtual environment;
  * install all python requirements;
  * install npm, bower, gulp;
  * install bower and npm requirements;
  * do gulp build;
  * do ./manage.py collectstatic;
  * start a server
